articles.title: Magnitude 6.3 earthquake strikes Turkey-Syria border region - EMSC - The Star Online
articles.description: (Reuters) -     A magnitude 6.3 earthquake at a depth of two km (1.2 miles) struck the Turkey-Syria border region on Monday, the European Mediterranean Seismological Centre (EMSC) said.
